
section.price-guarantee
  .price-guarantee-header
    // Example icon in the price-badge
    span.price-badge
      i.fas.fa-award
      | Price Guarantee

    h2 Our Price Match Guarantee
    p.guarantee-subtitle Our Promise to You

    p.guarantee-desc 
      | When you authorize us to work directly with your insurance company through our ACI agreement, 
      | we guarantee that your out-of-pocket expense won't exceed your insurance deductible.

    .guarantee-highlight 
      | You’ll only pay your deductible — nothing more. Plus, take advantage of our exclusive 
      | 12-month, 0% interest financing on your deductible.

  .guarantee-grid
    .guarantee-card
      .guarantee-card-header
        i.fas.fa-shield-alt.guarantee-icon
        h3.guarantee-title Zero Excess Cost
      p With our price guarantee, you’ll never pay more than your insurance deductible for covered repairs.

    .guarantee-card
      .guarantee-card-header
        i.fas.fa-credit-card.guarantee-icon
        h3.guarantee-title Deductible Financing
      p Finance your deductible with 0% interest for 12 months through our in-house financing program.

    .guarantee-card
      .guarantee-card-header
        i.fas.fa-money-bill-wave.guarantee-icon
        h3.guarantee-title Flexible Payments
      p Spread your deductible payments over 12 months with convenient monthly installments.

    .guarantee-card
      .guarantee-card-header
        i.fas.fa-handshake.guarantee-icon
        h3.guarantee-title Simple Process
      p No complicated paperwork or credit checks. Just sign the ACI and we handle the rest.

  .guarantee-cta
    a.btn.btn-primary(href="/services") 
      p See our services
      i.fas.fa-arrow-right
